quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  9,123,"Believers! wage war against such of the infidels as are your neighbours, and let them find you rigorous: and know that God is with those who fear him"
  9,124,"Whenever a Sura is sent down, there are some of them who say, \"Whose faith hath it increased?\" It will increase the faith of those who believe, and they shall rejoice"
  9,125,"But as to those in whose hearts is a disease, it will add doubt to their doubt, and they shall die infidels"
  9,126,"Do they not see that they are proved every year once or twice? Yet they turn not, neither are they warned"
  9,127,"And whenever a Sura is sent down, they look at one another. . . . \"Doth any one see you?\" then turn they aside. God shall turn their hearts aside, because they are a people devoid of understanding"
  9,128,"Now hath an Apostle come unto you from among yourselves: your iniquities press heavily upon him. He is careful over you, and towards the faithful, compassionate, merciful"
  9,129,"If they turn away, SAY: God sufficeth me: there is no God but He. In Him put I my trust. He is the possessor of the Glorious Throne"